            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para acceder a todas las variables de entorno, usamos el diccionario <code>os.environ</code>. Cada variable de entorno se almacena en este diccionario.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"import\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" os\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(os.environ)\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"27\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"environ({\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  &quot;API_KEY&quot;: &quot;12345-abcde-67890-fghij-12345&quot;,\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  &quot;SECRET_KEY&quot;: &quot;mysecretkey&quot;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  ...\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"})\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>environ</code>.</p></body></html>"
